{"sn9.6:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 9.6 ","sn9.6:0.2":"1. Vanavagga ","sn9.6:0.3":"Anuruddhasutta ","sn9.6:1.1":"Ekam samayam ayasma anuruddho kosalesu viharati annatarasmim vanasande. ","sn9.6:1.2":"Atha kho annatara tavatimsakayika devata jalini nama ayasmato anuruddhassa puranadutiyika yenayasma anuruddho tenupasankami; upasankamitva ayasmantam anuruddham gathaya ajjhabhasi: ","sn9.6:2.1":"“Tattha cittam panidhehi, ","sn9.6:2.2":"yattha te vusitam pure; ","sn9.6:2.3":"Tavatimsesu devesu, ","sn9.6:2.4":"sabbakamasamiddhisu; ","sn9.6:2.5":"Purakkhato parivuto, ","sn9.6:2.6":"devakannahi sobhasi”ti. ","sn9.6:3.1":"“Duggata devakannayo, ","sn9.6:3.2":"sakkayasmim patitthita; ","sn9.6:3.3":"Te capi duggata satta, ","sn9.6:3.4":"devakannahi patthita”ti. ","sn9.6:4.1":"“Na te sukham pajananti, ","sn9.6:4.2":"ye na passanti nandanam; ","sn9.6:4.3":"Avasam naradevanam, ","sn9.6:4.4":"tidasanam yasassinan”ti. ","sn9.6:5.1":"“Na tvam bale vijanasi, ","sn9.6:5.2":"yatha arahatam vaco; ","sn9.6:5.3":"Anicca sabbasankhara, ","sn9.6:5.4":"uppadavayadhammino; ","sn9.6:5.5":"Uppajjitva nirujjhanti, ","sn9.6:5.6":"tesam vupasamo sukho. ","sn9.6:6.1":"Natthi dani punavaso, ","sn9.6:6.2":"devakayasmi jalini; ","sn9.6:6.3":"Vikkhino jatisamsaro, ","sn9.6:6.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo”ti. "}